---
title: Soy-Glazed Steak with Sour Cream and Onion Mashed Potatoes and Sesame Spinach
description: A sweet and savory soy glaze gives this steak a winning finish. These mashed potatoes have sour cream for silkiness, making them hard to resist. Paired with sesame-infused spinach, this steak and potatoes twist is one you’ll be making again and again.
